<item>
            <title>[CXF-9114] ClientRequestContext#getConfiguration always return null in the MicroProfile RestClient</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-9114</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Calling ClientRequestContext#getConfiguration inside of a Filter when using the MicroProfile RestClient always return null, making it impossible to access properties set on the RestClientBuilder inside ClientRequest/ResponseFilters.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;To reproduce:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
@Path(&quot;&quot;)
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; GreetingClient {
    @GET
    Response greet();
}

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;Filter &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;implements&lt;/span&gt; ClientRequestFilter {
    @Override
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void filter(ClientRequestContext requestContext) {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;.out.println(requestContext.getConfiguration().getProperty(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt;));
    }
}

RestClientBuilder.newBuilder()
        .baseUri(URI.create(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;http:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//localhost:8080&quot;&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;        .property(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;bar&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
        .register(Filter.class)
        .build(GreetingClient.class)
        .greet();
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Stacktrace:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
